'''''Narra''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class T-4a shuttle]] used by [[Wraith Squadron]] during the campaign against [[Warlord/Legends|Warlord]] [[Zsinj]].

The shuttle was originally used by a former [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officer turned [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]], but was later captured and renamed by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. The vessel was largely stock, with the addition of a sophisticated electronically shielded secret smuggling compartment, similar to other smuggler's ships, such as the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']]. The compartment was at least big enough to fit an adult [[Gamorrean]], as well as parts for a jury rigged [[laser cannon]]. 

The smuggling compartment was used as the body for the [[Lunatic]], a makeshift [[Boarding craft/Legends|boarding craft]] piloted by [[Voort saBinring]] during the capture of the ''[[Ession Strike|Night Caller]]'' and was reinstalled after. This feature was also used to hide [[Eurrsk Thri'ag|Grinder]] during the mission to Revos on [[Storinal]] and by [[Castin Donn]] to sneak aboard the [[Iron Fist (Executor-class)|''Iron Fist'']].

